@@TJvCustomImageButton
Summary
  Base class for button controls with a window handle.
Description
  Use TJvCustomImageButton as a base class when creating new button controls with a handle.
  TJvCustomImageButton introduces support for new functionality not available in a standard TButton,
  like Wordwrap, a DropDownMenu and hot tracking.
  
  Several button controls in JVCL derives from TJvCustomImageButton, among them TJvImgBtn
See Also
  TJvImgBtn

